about important concepts

3
00:00:06,180 --> 00:00:09,580
and features which you need in Vue applications.

4
00:00:09,580 --> 00:00:11,210
There is one thing which is missing,

5
00:00:11,210 --> 00:00:14,630
which you don't need in any application,

6
