to provide a better user experience.

11
00:00:31,630 --> 00:00:33,130
Technically, transitions

12
00:00:33,130 --> 00:00:35,780
and animations are totally optional,

13
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:40,780
but they often make your UI and UX much, much better.

14
00:00:41,690 --> 00:00:43,030
And therefore in this module,

15
